00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:13,033
JIRAIYA: I'm coming in Tsunade.

4
00:00:13,066 --> 00:00:15,333
-Jiraiya, have you
learned anything?

5
00:00:15,366 --> 00:00:16,333
-I have.

6
00:00:16,366 --> 00:00:18,466
I've located the
leader of the Akatsuki.

7
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:19,500
-What?

8
00:00:19,533 --> 00:00:20,466
You have?

9
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:21,900
Tell me everything!

10
00:00:21,933 --> 00:00:24,800
-We can use this new information
to plan a surprise attack Lady

11
00:00:24,833 --> 00:00:25,833
Tsunade.

12
00:00:25,866 --> 00:00:27,666
-Now, now, don't be hasty.

13
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:30,233
-This isn't like plotting
a sequel to your novel.

14
00:00:30,266 --> 00:00:32,566
We don't have any
time to waste here.

15
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:34,433
-But haste makes waste.

16
00:00:34,466 --> 00:00:37,433
And we can't afford that,
especially not with the stakes

17
00:00:37,466 --> 00:00:39,466
as high as they are now.

18
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:42,300
Listen, why don't we go
somewhere, just the two of us?

