the middle of the day.

24
00:00:50,466 --> 00:00:52,666
What about all the
ninja out there on duty?

25
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:54,133
You should be
ashamed of yourself.

26
00:00:57,100 --> 00:00:58,466
Ah.

27
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:01,466
-You know, you really out
to take your own words

28
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,700
a bit more to heart Tsunade.

29
00:01:03,733 --> 00:01:06,033
I mean, downing that
sake straight out

30
00:01:06,066 --> 00:01:10,266
of the bottle-- like you
said, you are Hokage now.

31
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:11,133
[theme music]

32
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,040
-That girl is late again.

33
00:03:02,073 --> 00:03:05,173
How long does it take
to pick up supplies?

34
00:03:05,206 --> 00:03:08,373
-Oh, I wish it would
get dark already.

35
00:03:08,406 --> 00:03:10,506
When Jugo and
Suigetsu sleep I'll

36
00:03:10,540 --> 00:03:16,206
make my move on Sasuke.
(LAUGHING) I'm so excited.

37
00:03:21,206 --> 00:03:21,673
Oh.

38
00:03:26,706 --> 00:03:27,273
This feeling--

39
00:03:31,606 --> 00:03:34,240
-Kiba, what's the story?

40
00:03:34,273 --> 00:03:36,106
-Sasuke's scent is
faint and fading.

41
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:37,440
I need to concentrate.

42
00:03:37,473 --> 00:03:39,240
So shut up and stop
distracting me.

43
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:47,473
-Yep, they're coming, and fast.

44
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:53,473
One, two, their Chakra's
really strong too.

45
00:03:53,506 --> 00:03:55,706
And there's quite a lot of them.

46
00:04:00,606 --> 00:04:03,973
Not all of it human either.

47
00:04:04,006 --> 00:04:05,340
Dogs?

48
00:04:05,373 --> 00:04:06,906
So they're tracking
us by our scent?

49
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:12,273
Is it the Akatsuki
or the Hidden Leaf?

50
00:04:12,306 --> 00:04:16,940
-Jugo, I guess I better
go check on Karin.

51
00:04:16,973 --> 00:04:17,440
-Mm.

52
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,506
[grunting]

53
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:25,573
-Hey, get off me.

54
00:04:25,606 --> 00:04:27,040
-Wake up Sasuke.

55
00:04:27,073 --> 00:04:28,206
We're about to have company.

