wakes up, he's still dreamy.

57
00:04:33,706 --> 00:04:35,306
SASUKE (VOICEOVER):
Everyone get ready.

58
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:36,973
We're leaving.

59
00:04:37,006 --> 00:04:39,606
Jugo, mark the map with the
location of every Akatsuki

