would be a waste of our time.

74
00:05:20,940 --> 00:05:22,406
-That's exactly right.

75
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,306
Just forget about
the Hidden Leaf.

76
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:26,673
-So what's the plan then?

77
00:05:26,706 --> 00:05:28,873
-Itachi is our only priority.

78
00:05:28,906 --> 00:05:31,040
Then if worst comes
to worst, you three

79
00:05:31,073 --> 00:05:33,073
will stop the hidden leaf.

80
00:05:33,106 --> 00:05:35,240
For now, this is
team Heavy's mission.

81
00:05:35,273 --> 00:05:37,640
We're going to use the
intel that Jugo gathered.

82
00:05:37,673 --> 00:05:39,973
And we'll hit the Akatsuki
hideouts one by one.

83
00:05:40,006 --> 00:05:41,573
-All right, sounds good.

84
00:05:41,606 --> 00:05:42,373
-Let's do this.

85
00:05:47,973 --> 00:05:49,406
-Hmm?

86
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:51,406
-Hold on Jugo, help me out.

87
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,740
-With what?

88
00:05:52,773 --> 00:05:55,506
-I need you to gather as
many birds as you can.

89
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:56,140
-Why?

90
00:05:56,173 --> 00:05:57,273
What's your plan?

91
