-Well, this is one of
Sasuke's old outfits.

92
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:01,640
It's soaked with
his sweat and smell.

93
00:06:01,673 --> 00:06:02,773
So--

94
00:06:02,806 --> 00:06:04,140
-Wait, why did you hold
