Sensory type specialties are
different for each village.

102
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:23,840
The Hidden Leaf tend to use
Ninja Hounds for tracking.

103
00:06:23,873 --> 00:06:25,306
We can use that
to our advantage.

104
00:06:29,673 --> 00:06:31,040
-Kiba, what is it?

105
00:06:31,073 --> 00:06:32,040
-It's Sasuke.

106
00:06:32,073 --> 00:06:33,740
Shoot, looks like
he's on the move.

107
00:06:33,773 --> 00:06:35,606
-Then we better hurry
and get after him.

108
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,840
He's going after Itachi.

109
00:06:37,873 --> 00:06:40,106
-Hold on, something's wrong.

110
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:41,240
-What?

111
00:06:41,273 --> 00:06:43,040
-Sasuke's scent is
becoming more diffuse now.

112
00:06:43,073 --> 00:06:45,206
It's like it's scattering
outward in every direction

113
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,506
all at the same time.

114
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,873
He's sensed our movements.

115
00:06:47,906 --> 00:06:50,173
It's some kind of
strategic countermeasure.

116
00:06:50,206 --> 00:06:51,440
-He sensed us?

117
00:06:51,473 --> 00:06:52,840
But how?

118
00:06:52,873 --> 00:06:54,740
-I don't know exactly.

119
00:06:54,773 --> 00:06:57,373
But I think it's safe to assume
that he has a skilled Sensory

120
00:06:57,406 --> 00:06:59,673
Ninja on his team.

121
00:06:59,706 --> 00:07:01,173
-His scent is spreading too far.

122
00:07:01,206 --> 00:07:02,940
And our coms aren't long range.

123
00:07:02,973 --> 00:07:04,406
I'm the only one
who can track it.

124
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,740
But I don't know
which scent to follow.

125
00:07:06,773 --> 00:07:08,473
What do we do?

126
00:07:08,506 --> 00:07:10,106
-I'm going to find
him, even if I

127
00:07:10,140 --> 00:07:12,340
have to search every
blade of grass.

128
00:07:12,373 --> 00:07:13,906
I'll do whatever it takes.

129
00:07:13,940 --> 00:07:16,973
Just watch, Multi
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

130
00:07:25,206 --> 00:07:28,240
-It's just up ahead, huh?

131
00:07:28,273 --> 00:07:30,940
You three will wait here
until I give the order.

132
00:07:30,973 --> 00:07:31,940
I'll go check it out.

133
00:07:43,373 --> 00:07:46,640
NARUTO (VOICEOVER): Who's that?

134
00:07:46,673 --> 00:07:49,306
Sharingan.

135
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:49,806
Sasuke?

136
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:06,140
No, that's-- Itachi Uchiha.

137
00:08:10,606 --> 00:08:12,373
-Come on out, Naruto Uzumaki.

138
00:08:17,773 --> 00:08:20,173
-You're here to capture me, huh?

139
00:08:20,206 --> 00:08:22,440
-No, I'm not.

140
00:08:22,473 --> 00:08:25,473
