Ah, times have changed
and always will.

218
00:12:39,112 --> 00:12:40,612
You were so beautiful back then.

219
00:12:40,645 --> 00:12:43,845
And now, well, you're
a 50-something granny.

220
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:45,379
But does it pain
me to see how you

221
00:12:45,412 --> 00:12:47,679
