00:13:14,379 --> 00:13:17,779
To achieve that, I'd
gladly risk my life.

228
00:13:17,812 --> 00:13:21,012
Wisdom is the one thing that
makes growing old worth it.

229
00:13:42,875 --> 00:13:43,875
-What is this?

230
00:13:43,908 --> 00:13:45,308
What's going on here?

231
00:13:45,342 --> 00:13:47,875
I thought you said that
you weren't after me.

232
00:13:47,908 --> 00:13:49,842
Then why are you doing this?

233
00:13:49,875 --> 00:13:52,608
-I'm going now.

234
00:13:52,642 --> 00:13:54,742
I have an important
matter to attend to.

235
00:13:57,975 --> 00:14:03,442
A shadow clone, what
was that all about?

236
00:14:03,475 --> 00:14:05,908
-Damn, no luck with
this scent either.

237
00:14:11,875 --> 00:14:12,708
You OK Naruto?

238
00:14:12,742 --> 00:14:13,942
-Huh?

239
00:14:13,975 --> 00:14:16,708
