group, then how strong is he,

254
00:14:52,108 --> 00:14:54,242
I wonder?

255
00:14:54,275 --> 00:14:56,742
Jiraiya, this mission
of yours will take you

256
00:14:56,775 --> 00:14:58,742
right into the lion's den.

257
00:14:58,775 --> 00:15:03,708
-Well then, I think
I better get going.

258
00:15:03,742 --> 00:15:05,175
-Please come back alive Jiraiya.

259
00:15:08,008 --> 00:15:12,575
If I were to lose you too,
then I-- I don't know.

260
00:15:12,608 --> 00:15:14,275
-Are you saying
you'd cry for me?

261
00:15:14,308 --> 00:15:16,508
I'm glad to hear it.

262
00:15:16,542 --> 00:15:20,442
But I doubt it would be like
the time that Don died, right?

263
00:15:20,475 --> 00:15:22,008
-You idiot.

264
00:15:22,042 --> 00:15:26,375
-Say, how about
making a bet with me?

265
00:15:26,408 --> 00:15:29,308
You gamble everything
on me dying.

266
00:15:29,342 --> 00:15:31,542
After all, Tsunade, you
always lose your bets.

267
00:15:31,575 --> 00:15:32,942
Isn't that right?

268
00:15:35,742 --> 00:15:39,175
Promise me, if I do actually
manage to make it back alive--

269
00:15:49,208 --> 00:15:50,608
[laughter]

270
00:15:50,642 --> 00:15:53,175
-I'm only kidding Tsunade.

271
00:15:53,208 --> 00:15:54,975
You know, I'm grateful to you.

272
00:15:57,742 --> 00:16:00,508
Rejection makes a man stronger.

273
00:16:00,542 --> 00:16:03,175
I believe that you can't call
yourself a real man unless you

274
00:16:03,208 --> 00:16:06,408
can laugh off all the bad
stuff that happens to you.

275
00:16:06,442 --> 00:16:10,442
Or at least use it
as writing material.

276
00:16:10,475 --> 00:16:13,308
-So a man's only
job is to be strong?

277
00:16:13,342 --> 00:16:15,042
-Kind of.

278
00:16:15,075 --> 00:16:17,475
But that isn't the entire story.

279
00:16:17,508 --> 00:16:21,442
Basically, the pursuit of
happiness isn't for us.

280
00:16:21,475 --> 00:16:23,975
-Huh, stop trying
to act so cool.

281
00:16:24,008 --> 00:16:25,942
If there weren't any
women around there

282
00:16:25,975 --> 00:16:27,775
would be no rejection either.

283
00:16:27,808 --> 00:16:28,975
-Well, you have a point.

284
00:16:49,075 --> 00:16:53,042
-If anything happens contact
me through your toad.

285
00:16:53,075 --> 00:16:55,475
And I'll rush in
to help you myself.

286
00:16:55,508 --> 00:16:56,742
No need for that.

287
00:16:56,775 --> 00:16:59,642
You mustn't leave the village.

288
00:16:59,675 --> 00:17:03,442
All of the Hidden Leaf is
relying on you right now.

289
00:17:03,475 --> 00:17:05,742
Plenty of others
could be Hokage.

290
00:17:05,775 --> 00:17:08,408
-But there can be no
stability if the leadership

291
00:17:08,442 --> 00:17:10,208
keeps changing.

292
00:17:10,242 --> 00:17:13,042
And right now, there's no
better Hokage in the Hidden Leaf

293
00:17:13,075 --> 00:17:14,808
Village than you Tsunade.

294
00:17:14,842 --> 00:17:18,542
-No, there's Kakashi and
well, eventually Naruto

295
00:17:18,575 --> 00:17:20,542
could become Hokage as well.

296
00:17:20,575 --> 00:17:23,408
-Uh-huh, boy, you really
are sold on Naruto.

297
00:17:23,442 --> 00:17:23,975
Aren't you?

298
00:17:27,308 --> 00:17:30,142
Although I can see why.

299
00:17:30,175 --> 00:17:32,542
Your kid brother, not lucky.

300
00:17:32,575 --> 00:17:33,642
Your boyfriend, Don.

301
00:17:38,308 --> 00:17:39,808
I'll be Hokage.

302
00:17:39,842 --> 00:17:40,808
That's my dream.

303
00:17:46,442 --> 00:17:49,942
And Naruto too,
all three of them,

304
00:17:49,975 --> 00:17:53,208
chasing after the same dream.

305
00:17:53,242 --> 00:17:56,008
So there's Kakashi
and Naruto, maybe.

306
00:17:56,042 --> 00:17:57,542
You may have given
him your necklace.

307
00:17:57,575 --> 00:17:59,542
But he still has
a long way to go.

308
00:17:59,575 --> 00:18:01,008
-You believe in him too.

309
00:18:01,042 --> 00:18:03,642
That's why you pushed him
so hard drive Jiraiya.

310
00:18:03,675 --> 00:18:06,008
I mean, you even taught
him the Rasengan.

311
00:18:06,042 --> 00:18:06,975
[laughing]

312
00:18:07,008 --> 00:18:09,175
-Just put it down to nostalgia.

313
00:18:09,208 --> 00:18:12,675
He reminded of the days
when I taught Minato.

314
00:18:12,708 --> 00:18:17,575
-Minato Namikaze,
Naruto's just like him.

315
00:18:17,608 --> 00:18:21,942
-Minato was a
once-in-a-generation genius.

316
00:18:21,975 --> 00:18:24,542
There won't be
another like him ever.

317
00:18:24,575 --> 00:18:28,342
He was kind and gentle, yet
fierce and full of grit,

318
00:18:28,375 --> 00:18:31,608
became the fourth Hokage
in the blink of an eye.

319
00:18:31,642 --> 00:18:34,042
Now, I've never been
a parent before.

320
00:18:34,075 --> 00:18:36,975
So I don't know all that much
about these kinds of things.

321
00:18:37,008 --> 00:18:39,308
But if he'd been my
son, I'd be very proud.

322
00:18:39,342 --> 00:18:40,475
[laughing]

323
00:18:40,508 --> 00:18:43,075
-Now that you mention
it, Naruto might not

324
00:18:43,108 --> 00:18:44,708
be like him after all.

325
00:18:44,742 --> 00:18:47,075
He's not the kind of
child you boast about.

326
00:18:47,108 --> 00:18:50,408
He's the one whose mischief
you always try to cover up.

327
00:18:50,442 --> 00:18:54,575
No, I would say, Naruto is
more like his mother was.

328
00:18:54,608 --> 00:18:58,308
-Wasn't she a kunoichi
from the land of Eddies?

329
00:18:58,342 --> 00:19:02,508
That's right, his personality
is just like Kushina Uzumaki.

330
00:19:02,542 --> 00:19:05,508
-That's right, I had
forgotten her name.

331
00:19:05,542 --> 00:19:07,608
She was a chatty
red-haired little rascal.

332
00:19:07,642 --> 00:19:10,742
And was quite a
tomboy, as I remember.

333
00:19:10,775 --> 00:19:11,908
-She was that.

334
00:19:11,942 --> 00:19:13,608
But she grew up to
be a real beauty.

335
00:19:13,642 --> 00:19:16,408
But Naruto looks
more like his father.

336
00:19:16,442 --> 00:19:20,342
-Yeah, when I look at Naruto
I see a lot of his father.

337
00:19:20,375 --> 00:19:22,375
Although to me,
it feels as if I'm

338
00:19:22,408 --> 00:19:25,308
looking at my very own grandson.

339
00:19:25,342 --> 00:19:28,775
-It's being passed on,
the Will of the Leaf,

340
00:19:28,808 --> 00:19:30,542
from past to future.

341
00:19:38,042 --> 00:19:39,508
[gasps]

342
00:19:43,042 --> 00:19:44,775
-Now, I really
ought to get going.

343
00:19:49,375 --> 00:19:52,375
Oh, that's right.

344
00:19:52,408 --> 00:19:54,975
I had one last warning.

345
00:19:55,008 --> 00:19:56,608
-What?

346
00:19:56,642 --> 00:19:59,775
-Beware of The
Foundation Tsunade.

347
00:19:59,808 --> 00:20:01,908
-Yes, I know.

348
00:20:01,942 --> 00:20:03,275
-Good.

349
00:20:03,308 --> 00:20:09,575
Then-- See ya.

350
00:20:30,108 --> 00:20:31,575
[theme music]

351
00:22:03,410 --> 00:22:05,910
-Anyone who's far
away, listen carefully.

352
00:22:05,943 --> 00:22:09,110
And anyone who's close,
come even closer and see.

353
00:22:09,143 --> 00:22:12,743
I am the sizzling handsome
ninja of the Hidden Leaf.

354
00:22:12,777 --> 00:22:15,643
I'm the one all the girls
cheer so wildly for.

355
00:22:15,677 --> 00:22:17,310
I'm smooth enough to
steal your hearts,

356
00:22:17,343 --> 00:22:19,643
but so strong I'll never break.

357
00:22:19,677 --> 00:22:21,810
I help the weak and
fight the strong.

358
00:22:21,843 --> 00:22:25,543
Now, let the tail of
Jiraiya Ninja Scrolls begin!

359
00:22:25,577 --> 00:22:27,910
Next time, Tales
of a Gutsy Ninja,

360
00:22:27,943 --> 00:22:30,443
Jiraiya Ninja Scrolls, part one.

361
00:22:36,277 --> 00:22:38,077
-All right, today's guest--

362
00:22:38,110 --> 00:22:39,477
-Now, just wait right there.

363
00:22:39,510 --> 00:22:42,677
I am the most holy hermit sage
of the spirit of Mount Myoboku

364
00:22:42,710 --> 00:22:44,010
Toads.

365
00:22:44,043 --> 00:22:46,943
Yes, I am the great, wise,
and powerful master, Jiraiya.

366
00:22:46,977 --> 00:22:47,877
-Oh great, it's you.

367
00:22:47,910 --> 00:22:49,510
-What a greeting.

368
00:22:49,543 --> 00:22:51,277
Aren't you happy to see me?

369
00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:52,243
-Well, it's not that.

370
00:22:52,277 --> 00:22:53,610
I just don't think
that we really

371
00:22:53,643 --> 00:22:55,010
have very much to talk about.

372
00:22:55,043 --> 00:22:56,143
-Oh, don't say that.

373
00:22:56,177 --> 00:22:58,877
What about revisiting
all my heroic tales?

374
00:22:58,910 --> 00:23:00,077
Heroic tales?

375
00:23:00,110 --> 00:23:01,843
-They'll make all the
women shout with joy

376
00:23:01,877 --> 00:23:03,643
while they watch TV.

377
00:23:03,677 --> 00:23:06,277
-Like long ago, when you
peaked into the Hot Springs

378
00:23:06,310 --> 00:23:07,510
and got busted?

379
00:23:07,543 --> 00:23:10,343
Or when the third Hokage
made you kneel for hours?

380
00:23:10,377 --> 00:23:12,910
Or that time you had a book
signing for your first novel

381
00:23:12,943 --> 00:23:17,177
and not one person bought
a copy or even showed up?

382
00:23:17,210 --> 00:23:19,077
-Surely there must
be some others.

383
00:23:19,110 --> 00:23:21,410
-Hmm, I can't think of one.

384
00:23:21,443 --> 00:23:23,643
-That'll all I am
to you, isn't it?

385
00:23:23,677 --> 00:23:24,377
Just some joke?

386
00:23:24,410 --> 00:23:25,210
-Oh--

387
00:23:25,243 --> 00:23:26,810
-That's it, tell them that one!

388
00:23:26,843 --> 00:23:28,343
-Sorry, our time's up now.

389
00:23:28,377 --> 00:23:30,310
So see you later.

390
00:23:30,343 --> 00:23:32,610
-What the hell?

